modName: Witcher2 Retexture of L0RD0FWars Craftable Seltkirk Armor
summary: Redanian retexture for Craftable Seltkirk Armor
descriptionHtml:
This is a Nexus Exclusive Mod, don\'t reupload it anywhere!

This mod is ONLY a retexture and NOT a Mod with .esp files and meshes.
The Redanian retexture is one of my retextures, that I have made for a long time.
you need the original mod from L0RD0FWAR for this.

INSTALLATION:
1. Download this: http://www.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/5588#
2. delete the original texture, copy and paste my retexture on the texture folder from seltkirk\'s armor and change the name to Armor_01.
3. enjoy :)
author: Witcher5688
